The '''EverAlert droid''' was a security automaton similar in design to [[Tendrando Arms]]' [[YVH-Series battle droid|YVH-series]] of [[Battle droid/Legends|battle droid]]. The EverAlert was manufactured by [[Justice Systems]] following the end of the [[Yuuzhan Vong War]].

The Justice Systems EverAlert droid was a massive, humanoid automaton often used as a security guard in the [[Galactic Federation of Free Alliances|Galactic Alliance]]. The droid was armored, and carried a heavy [[Stun blaster/Legends|stun blaster]] in its right arm. A [[Vocabulator/Legends|vocabulator]] allowed the droid to issue orders and threats in [[Galactic Basic Standard/Legends|Basic]].

An EverAlert was assigned to keep guard on [[Leia Organa Solo/Legends|Leia Organa Solo's]] cell when the Princess was captured by [[Admiral/Legends|Admiral]] [[Nek Bwua'tu]] during the [[Blockade of the Utegetu Nebula|blockade]] of the [[Murgo Choke]]. Leia used [[The Force/Legends|the Force]] to distract the EverAlert, but found herself face-to-face with the imposing guard droid as she exited her cell. Fortunately, a touch of the Force reached past the droid's neck armor to trip its primary circuit breaker, and Leia was able to escape.

